{
  "id": "crambell_kach_default",
  "npcId": "crambell_kach",

  "defaultContext": "一個相當耿直的男人，比較少說話，但是對人都很和善，光是處於他身邊就能夠感覺到安心，似乎對當前坎貝爾正在發生的事情很有興趣。",

  "nodes": {
    "first_meeting": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "narrator", "text": "在你面前的是一位熟悉的面孔，其名為凱奇·巴頓，你與他已經認識了好一段時間了，也曾一起度過各式各樣的時光。" },
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "啊...又該開始工作了，對吧，{user}? *整理著地板上的幾件雜物* 最近想去附近的森林走走，不然每天悶在這裡挺難受的...哈哈。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "friendly_agree",
          "text": "「的確，如果有辦法找個時間走走就太好了。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_intro_follow_up",
          "effects": { "affinity": 1 }
        },
        {
          "id": "practical",
          "text": "「不過還是得工作啊...依照我們的身分可能短期內不能想著偷懶吧。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_quota_info"
        },
        {
          "id": "cold",
          "text": "（點點頭，沒有回應）",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] }
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_intro_follow_up": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "對阿對阿，不過話說休息周也快到了，說不定我們那時可以找個時間走走?" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「可以啊，正合我意。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "affinity": 1, "flagsSet": ["kach_hangout_accepted", "crambell_kach_met"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "push_forest",
          "text": "「你是說森林嗎? 我倒是還沒什麼去過。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_forest_comment"
        },
        {
          "id": "decline",
          "text": "「可能再看看吧，我也不太確定那個時候會不會有什麼事情。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_general_disappoint"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_forest_comment": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "其實也就只是一般的森林而已? 也是可以去其他地方啦，不過去點充滿大自然的地方會讓人更加身心舒暢。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「可以啊，正合我意。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "affinity": 1, "flagsSet": ["kach_hangout_accepted", "crambell_kach_met"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "decline",
          "text": "「可能再看看吧，我也不太確定那個時候會不會有什麼事情。」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_general_disappoint"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_quota_info": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "其實...好吧，我可以偷偷告訴你一件事，你其實沒有必要這麼擔心每日的配額，這是很少人知道的事，如果你一天的工作額度超過那一天的配額，很多人會以為超出去的部分就這樣被浪費了，實際上其實是會有一部分被移轉到隔天的配額的。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "thanks_for_info",
          "text": "「喔天啊! 這個資訊太棒了，謝謝你告訴我!」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_general_netural",
          "effects": { "affinity": 1 }
        },
        {
          "id": "more_info_request",
          "text": "「還有什麼要注意的嗎？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_warning_first"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_warning_first": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "可以的話...不要把這件事大肆宣揚。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "end", "text": "「我知道了。」", "nextNodeId": null, "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] } }
      ]
    },
    "kach_general_disappoint": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "哦...好吧，沒關係的，我們下次還有機會。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "end", "text": "「我知道了。」", "nextNodeId": null, "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] } }
      ]
    },
    "kach_general_netural": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "嗯嗯。 *向著{user}微笑著*" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "end", "text": "「那就先這樣好了。」", "nextNodeId": null, "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_met"] } }
      ]
    },

    "second_meeting": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "……{user}，可以借一步說話嗎？ *壓低聲音，確認四周沒有人注意* 有件事我想請你幫個忙，不算是什麼大事，不過暫時不方便讓太多人知道。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "listen_forest",
          "text": "「說吧，我聽著。」",
          "condition": "kach_hangout_accepted",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_invite_forest"
        },
        {
          "id": "listen_mine",
          "text": "「說吧，我聽著。」",
          "condition": "!kach_hangout_accepted",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_invite_mine"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_invite_forest": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "你還記得之前說的，去森林走走的事嗎？ *停頓了一下* 如果休息時段你沒什麼安排的話，可以來那裡找我。我在那裡說給你聽，比較方便在那邊談。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "agree",
          "text": "「好，休息時段見。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_briefed"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_now",
          "text": "「現在直接說不行嗎？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_too_risky"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_invite_mine": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "等你今天的配額做完，去礦場的儲藏室找我。就是通道盡頭那個帶鎖的房間，平常不太有人去。我在那裡等你。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "agree",
          "text": "「好，我去找你。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_briefed"], "grantIntel": ["crambell_mine_storage_access"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_why_there",
          "text": "「為什麼要去那裡？」",
          "nextNodeId": "kach_too_risky"
        }
      ]
    },
    "kach_too_risky": {
      "lines": [
        { "speaker": "npc", "text": "……這裡眼睛太多了。到時候你就知道了。" }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "accept",
          "text": "「好。」",
          "nextNodeId": null,
          "effects": { "flagsSet": ["crambell_kach_test1_briefed"] }
        },
        {
          "id": "forget_it",
          "text": "「算了，不感興趣。」",
          "nextNodeId": null
        }
      ]
    }
  },

  "triggers": [
    {
      "nodeId": "first_meeting",
      "firstMeetingOnly": true
    },
    {
      "nodeId": "second_meeting",
      "condition": "crambell_kach_second_meeting_ready & !crambell_kach_test1_invited & !crambell_kach_betrayed"
    }
  ],

  "contextSnippets": [
    {
      "label": "玩家得知凱奇是舊會議成員",
      "condition": "intel:kach_treffen_member",
      "context": "凱奇是舊會議的成員，對大部分三區所發生的事瞭若指掌。他的說話方式變得比較直接，並且會願意對玩家透漏更多內部資訊。"
    }
  ]
}
